TopicTitle: Some minor problems with the B9 Aerospace pack.

Articles.Content:
These are some relatively minor problems with this pack, The Sabre Engines don't work, and the IVA views in the cockpit don't display flight information Real time.

This was an issue when B9 was my only Mod installed, So I have doubts about Compatibility issues.

My Mod list just Incase of compatibility Issues:

- B9 Pack (Duh lol)

- FAR

- Kethane

- KW Rocketry

- Kerbal Engineer

- Active Texture Management

- Deadly Reentry

- Enhanced Navball

- KAS

- SCANsat

- Habitat Pack

- Procedural Fairings

- MK2 Cockpit IVA
